1652template <class V, ENUM_REGIME FlowRegime>
1653void CFVMFlowSolverBase<V, FlowRegime>::SetResidual_DualTime(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
1654 CConfig *config, unsigned short iRKStep, unsigned short iMesh,
1655 unsigned short RunTime_EqSystem) {
1656 /*--- Local variables ---*/
1657
1658 unsigned short iVar, iMarker, iDim, iNeigh;
1659 unsigned long iPoint, jPoint, iEdge, iVertex;
1660
1661 const su2double *U_time_nM1 = nullptr, *U_time_n = nullptr, *U_time_nP1 = nullptr;
1662 su2double Volume_nM1, Volume_nP1, TimeStep;
1663 const su2double *Normal = nullptr, *GridVel_i = nullptr, *GridVel_j = nullptr;
1664 su2double Residual_GCL;
1665
1666 const bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
1667 const bool first_order = (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST);
1668 const bool second_order = (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_2ND);
1669
1670 /*--- Store the physical time step ---*/
1671
1672 TimeStep = config->GetDelta_UnstTimeND();
1673
1674 /*--- Compute the dual time-stepping source term for static meshes ---*/
1675
1676 if (!dynamic_grid) {
1677
1678 /*--- Loop over all nodes (excluding halos) ---*/
1679
1680 AD::StartNoSharedReading();
1681
1682 SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
1683 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
1684
1685 /*--- Retrieve the solution at time levels n-1, n, and n+1. Note that
1686 we are currently iterating on U^n+1 and that U^n & U^n-1 are fixed,
1687 previous solutions that are stored in memory. ---*/
1688
1689 U_time_nM1 = nodes->GetSolution_time_n1(iPoint);
1690 U_time_n = nodes->GetSolution_time_n(iPoint);
1691 U_time_nP1 = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint);
1692
1693 /*--- CV volume at time n+1. As we are on a static mesh, the volume
1694 of the CV will remained fixed for all time steps. ---*/
1695
1696 Volume_nP1 = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
1697
1698 /*--- Compute the dual time-stepping source term based on the chosen
1699 time discretization scheme (1st- or 2nd-order).---*/
1700
1701 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1702 if (first_order)
1703 LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar) += (U_time_nP1[iVar] - U_time_n[iVar])*Volume_nP1 / TimeStep;
1704 if (second_order)
1705 LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar) += ( 3.0*U_time_nP1[iVar] - 4.0*U_time_n[iVar]
1706 +1.0*U_time_nM1[iVar])*Volume_nP1 / (2.0*TimeStep);
1707 }
1708
1709 /*--- Compute the Jacobian contribution due to the dual time source term. ---*/
1710 if (implicit) {
1711 if (first_order) Jacobian.AddVal2Diag(iPoint, Volume_nP1/TimeStep);
1712 if (second_order) Jacobian.AddVal2Diag(iPoint, (Volume_nP1*3.0)/(2.0*TimeStep));
1713 }
1714 }
1715 END_SU2_OMP_FOR
1716
1717 AD::EndNoSharedReading();
1718
1719 }
1720
1721 else {
1722
1723 /*--- For unsteady flows on dynamic meshes (rigidly transforming or
1724 dynamically deforming), the Geometric Conservation Law (GCL) should be
1725 satisfied in conjunction with the ALE formulation of the governing
1726 equations. The GCL prevents accuracy issues caused by grid motion, i.e.
1727 a uniform free-stream should be preserved through a moving grid. First,
1728 we will loop over the edges and boundaries to compute the GCL component
1729 of the dual time source term that depends on grid velocities. ---*/
1730
1731 SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
1732 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; ++iPoint) {
1733
1734 GridVel_i = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
1735 U_time_n = nodes->GetSolution_time_n(iPoint);
1736
1737 for (iNeigh = 0; iNeigh < geometry->nodes->GetnPoint(iPoint); iNeigh++) {
1738
1739 iEdge = geometry->nodes->GetEdge(iPoint, iNeigh);
1740 Normal = geometry->edges->GetNormal(iEdge);
1741
1742 jPoint = geometry->nodes->GetPoint(iPoint, iNeigh);
1743 GridVel_j = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(jPoint);
1744
1745 /*--- Determine whether to consider the normal outward or inward. ---*/
1746 su2double dir = (iPoint < jPoint)? 0.5 : -0.5;
1747
1748 Residual_GCL = 0.0;
1749 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1750 Residual_GCL += dir*(GridVel_i[iDim]+GridVel_j[iDim])*Normal[iDim];
1751
1752 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1753 LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar) += U_time_n[iVar]*Residual_GCL;
1754 }
1755 }
1756 END_SU2_OMP_FOR
1757
1758 /*--- Loop over the boundary edges ---*/
1759
1760 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < geometry->GetnMarker(); iMarker++) {
1761 if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) != INTERNAL_BOUNDARY) &&
1762 (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) != NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY) &&
1763 (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) != PERIODIC_BOUNDARY)) {
1764
1765 SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
1766 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
1767
1768 /*--- Get the index for node i plus the boundary face normal ---*/
1769
1770 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1771 Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
1772
1773 /*--- Grid velocities stored at boundary node i ---*/
1774
1775 GridVel_i = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
1776
1777 /*--- Compute the GCL term by dotting the grid velocity with the face
1778 normal. The normal is negated to match the boundary convention. ---*/
1779
1780 Residual_GCL = 0.0;
1781 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1782 Residual_GCL -= 0.5*(GridVel_i[iDim]+GridVel_i[iDim])*Normal[iDim];
1783
1784 /*--- Compute the GCL component of the source term for node i ---*/
1785
1786 U_time_n = nodes->GetSolution_time_n(iPoint);
1787 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
1788 LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar) += U_time_n[iVar]*Residual_GCL;
1789 }
1790 END_SU2_OMP_FOR
1791 }
1792 }
1793
1794 /*--- Loop over all nodes (excluding halos) to compute the remainder
1795 of the dual time-stepping source term. ---*/
1796
1797 AD::StartNoSharedReading();
1798
1799 SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
1800 for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
1801
1802 /*--- Retrieve the solution at time levels n-1, n, and n+1. Note that
1803 we are currently iterating on U^n+1 and that U^n & U^n-1 are fixed,
1804 previous solutions that are stored in memory. ---*/
1805
1806 U_time_nM1 = nodes->GetSolution_time_n1(iPoint);
1807 U_time_n = nodes->GetSolution_time_n(iPoint);
1808 U_time_nP1 = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint);
1809
1810 /*--- CV volume at time n-1 and n+1. In the case of dynamically deforming
1811 grids, the volumes will change. On rigidly transforming grids, the
1812 volumes will remain constant. ---*/
1813
1814 Volume_nM1 = geometry->nodes->GetVolume_nM1(iPoint);
1815 Volume_nP1 = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
1816
1817 /*--- Compute the dual time-stepping source residual. Due to the
1818 introduction of the GCL term above, the remainder of the source residual
1819 due to the time discretization has a new form.---*/
1820
1821 for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
1822 if (first_order)
1823 LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar) += (U_time_nP1[iVar] - U_time_n[iVar])*(Volume_nP1/TimeStep);
1824 if (second_order)
1825 LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar) += (U_time_nP1[iVar] - U_time_n[iVar])*(3.0*Volume_nP1/(2.0*TimeStep))
1826 + (U_time_nM1[iVar] - U_time_n[iVar])*(Volume_nM1/(2.0*TimeStep));
1827 }
1828
1829 /*--- Compute the Jacobian contribution due to the dual time source term. ---*/
1830 if (implicit) {
1831 if (first_order) Jacobian.AddVal2Diag(iPoint, Volume_nP1/TimeStep);
1832 if (second_order) Jacobian.AddVal2Diag(iPoint, (Volume_nP1*3.0)/(2.0*TimeStep));
1833 }
1834 }
1835 END_SU2_OMP_FOR
1836
1837 AD::EndNoSharedReading();
1838 }
1839
1840}
1841
1842template <class V, ENUM_REGIME FlowRegime>
1843void CFVMFlowSolverBase<V, FlowRegime>::Pressure_Forces(const CGeometry* geometry, const CConfig* config) {
1844 unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
1845 unsigned short iDim, iMarker, Boundary, Monitoring, iMarker_Monitoring;
1846 su2double Pressure = 0.0, NFPressOF, RefPressure;
1847 const su2double *Normal = nullptr, *Coord = nullptr;
1848 string Marker_Tag, Monitoring_Tag;
1849 su2double AxiFactor;
1850
1851 su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA() * PI_NUMBER / 180.0;
1852 su2double Beta = config->GetAoS() * PI_NUMBER / 180.0;
1853 su2double RefArea = config->GetRefArea();
1854 su2double RefLength = config->GetRefLength();
1855 auto Origin = config->GetRefOriginMoment(0);
1856 bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
1857
1858 SetReferenceValues(*config);
1859
1860 const su2double factor = 1.0 / AeroCoeffForceRef;
1861
1862 /*--- Reference pressure is always the far-field value. ---*/
1863
1864 RefPressure = Pressure_Inf;
1865
1866 /*-- Variables initialization ---*/
1867
1868 TotalCoeff.setZero();
1869
1870 Total_CNearFieldOF = 0.0;
1871 Total_Heat = 0.0;
1872 Total_MaxHeat = 0.0;
1873
1874 AllBoundInvCoeff.setZero();
1875
1876 AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv = 0.0;
1877
1878 SurfaceInvCoeff.setZero();
1879 SurfaceCoeff.setZero();
1880
1881 /*--- Loop over the Euler and Navier-Stokes markers ---*/
1882
1883 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
1884 Boundary = config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker);
1885 Monitoring = config->GetMarker_All_Monitoring(iMarker);
1886
1887 /*--- Obtain the origin for the moment computation for a particular marker ---*/
1888
1889 if (Monitoring == YES) {
1890 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
1891 Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring_TagBound(iMarker_Monitoring);
1892 Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
1893 if (Marker_Tag == Monitoring_Tag) Origin = config->GetRefOriginMoment(iMarker_Monitoring);
1894 }
1895 }
1896
1897 if (config->GetSolid_Wall(iMarker) || (Boundary == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY) || (Boundary == INLET_FLOW) ||
1898 (Boundary == OUTLET_FLOW) || (Boundary == ACTDISK_INLET) || (Boundary == ACTDISK_OUTLET) ||
1899 (Boundary == ENGINE_INFLOW) || (Boundary == ENGINE_EXHAUST)) {
1900 /*--- Forces initialization at each Marker ---*/
1901
1902 InvCoeff.setZero(iMarker);
1903
1904 CNearFieldOF_Inv[iMarker] = 0.0;
1905
1906 su2double ForceInviscid[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, MomentInviscid[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
1907 su2double MomentX_Force[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, MomentY_Force[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, MomentZ_Force[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
1908
1909 NFPressOF = 0.0;
1910
1911 /*--- Loop over the vertices to compute the forces ---*/
1912
1913 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
1914 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1915
1916 Pressure = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
1917
1918 CPressure[iMarker][iVertex] = (Pressure - RefPressure) * factor * RefArea;
1919
1920 /*--- Note that the pressure coefficient is computed at the
1921 halo cells (for visualization purposes), but not the forces ---*/
1922
1923 if ((geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) && (Monitoring == YES)) {
1924 Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
1925 Coord = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
1926
1927 /*--- Quadratic objective function for the near-field.
1928 This uses the infinity pressure regardless of Mach number. ---*/
1929
1930 NFPressOF += 0.5 * (Pressure - Pressure_Inf) * (Pressure - Pressure_Inf) * Normal[nDim - 1];
1931
1932 su2double MomentDist[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
1933 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1934 MomentDist[iDim] = Coord[iDim] - Origin[iDim];
1935 }
1936
1937 /*--- Axisymmetric simulations ---*/
1938
1939 if (axisymmetric)
1940 AxiFactor = 2.0 * PI_NUMBER * geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1);
1941 else
1942 AxiFactor = 1.0;
1943
1944 /*--- Force computation, note the minus sign due to the
1945 orientation of the normal (outward) ---*/
1946
1947 su2double Force[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
1948 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1949 Force[iDim] = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf) * Normal[iDim] * factor * AxiFactor;
1950 ForceInviscid[iDim] += Force[iDim];
1951 }
1952
1953 /*--- Moment with respect to the reference axis ---*/
1954
1955 if (nDim == 3) {
1956 MomentInviscid[0] += (Force[2] * MomentDist[1] - Force[1] * MomentDist[2]) / RefLength;
1957 MomentX_Force[1] += (-Force[1] * Coord[2]);
1958 MomentX_Force[2] += (Force[2] * Coord[1]);
1959
1960 MomentInviscid[1] += (Force[0] * MomentDist[2] - Force[2] * MomentDist[0]) / RefLength;
1961 MomentY_Force[2] += (-Force[2] * Coord[0]);
1962 MomentY_Force[0] += (Force[0] * Coord[2]);
1963 }
1964 MomentInviscid[2] += (Force[1] * MomentDist[0] - Force[0] * MomentDist[1]) / RefLength;
1965 MomentZ_Force[0] += (-Force[0] * Coord[1]);
1966 MomentZ_Force[1] += (Force[1] * Coord[0]);
1967 }
1968 }
1969
1970 /*--- Project forces and store the non-dimensional coefficients ---*/
1971
1972 if (Monitoring == YES) {
1973 if (Boundary != NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY) {
1974 if (nDim == 2) {
1975 InvCoeff.CD[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[0] * cos(Alpha) + ForceInviscid[1] * sin(Alpha);
1976 InvCoeff.CL[iMarker] = -ForceInviscid[0] * sin(Alpha) + ForceInviscid[1] * cos(Alpha);
1977 InvCoeff.CEff[iMarker] = InvCoeff.CL[iMarker] / (InvCoeff.CD[iMarker] + EPS);
1978 InvCoeff.CMz[iMarker] = MomentInviscid[2];
1979 InvCoeff.CoPx[iMarker] = MomentZ_Force[1];
1980 InvCoeff.CoPy[iMarker] = -MomentZ_Force[0];
1981 InvCoeff.CFx[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[0];
1982 InvCoeff.CFy[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[1];
1983 InvCoeff.CT[iMarker] = -InvCoeff.CFx[iMarker];
1984 InvCoeff.CQ[iMarker] = -InvCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
1985 InvCoeff.CMerit[iMarker] = InvCoeff.CT[iMarker] / (InvCoeff.CQ[iMarker] + EPS);
1986 }
1987 if (nDim == 3) {
1988 InvCoeff.CD[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[0] * cos(Alpha) * cos(Beta) + ForceInviscid[1] * sin(Beta) +
1989 ForceInviscid[2] * sin(Alpha) * cos(Beta);
1990 InvCoeff.CL[iMarker] = -ForceInviscid[0] * sin(Alpha) + ForceInviscid[2] * cos(Alpha);
1991 InvCoeff.CSF[iMarker] = -ForceInviscid[0] * sin(Beta) * cos(Alpha) + ForceInviscid[1] * cos(Beta) -
1992 ForceInviscid[2] * sin(Beta) * sin(Alpha);
1993 InvCoeff.CEff[iMarker] = InvCoeff.CL[iMarker] / (InvCoeff.CD[iMarker] + EPS);
1994 InvCoeff.CMx[iMarker] = MomentInviscid[0];
1995 InvCoeff.CMy[iMarker] = MomentInviscid[1];
1996 InvCoeff.CMz[iMarker] = MomentInviscid[2];
1997 InvCoeff.CoPx[iMarker] = -MomentY_Force[0];
1998 InvCoeff.CoPz[iMarker] = MomentY_Force[2];
1999 InvCoeff.CFx[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[0];
2000 InvCoeff.CFy[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[1];
2001 InvCoeff.CFz[iMarker] = ForceInviscid[2];
2002 InvCoeff.CT[iMarker] = -InvCoeff.CFz[iMarker];
2003 InvCoeff.CQ[iMarker] = -InvCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2004 InvCoeff.CMerit[iMarker] = InvCoeff.CT[iMarker] / (InvCoeff.CQ[iMarker] + EPS);
2005 }
2006
2007 AllBoundInvCoeff.CD += InvCoeff.CD[iMarker];
2008 AllBoundInvCoeff.CL += InvCoeff.CL[iMarker];
2009 AllBoundInvCoeff.CSF += InvCoeff.CSF[iMarker];
2010 AllBoundInvCoeff.CEff = AllBoundInvCoeff.CL / (AllBoundInvCoeff.CD + EPS);
2011 AllBoundInvCoeff.CMx += InvCoeff.CMx[iMarker];
2012 AllBoundInvCoeff.CMy += InvCoeff.CMy[iMarker];
2013 AllBoundInvCoeff.CMz += InvCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2014 AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPx += InvCoeff.CoPx[iMarker];
2015 AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPy += InvCoeff.CoPy[iMarker];
2016 AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPz += InvCoeff.CoPz[iMarker];
2017 AllBoundInvCoeff.CFx += InvCoeff.CFx[iMarker];
2018 AllBoundInvCoeff.CFy += InvCoeff.CFy[iMarker];
2019 AllBoundInvCoeff.CFz += InvCoeff.CFz[iMarker];
2020 AllBoundInvCoeff.CT += InvCoeff.CT[iMarker];
2021 AllBoundInvCoeff.CQ += InvCoeff.CQ[iMarker];
2022 AllBoundInvCoeff.CMerit = AllBoundInvCoeff.CT / (AllBoundInvCoeff.CQ + EPS);
2023
2024 /*--- Compute the coefficients per surface ---*/
2025
2026 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
2027 Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring_TagBound(iMarker_Monitoring);
2028 Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
2029 if (Marker_Tag == Monitoring_Tag) {
2030 SurfaceInvCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] += InvCoeff.CL[iMarker];
2031 SurfaceInvCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] += InvCoeff.CD[iMarker];
2032 SurfaceInvCoeff.CSF[iMarker_Monitoring] += InvCoeff.CSF[iMarker];
2033 SurfaceInvCoeff.CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceInvCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] / (SurfaceInvCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
2034 SurfaceInvCoeff.CFx[iMarker_Monitoring] += InvCoeff.CFx[iMarker];
2035 SurfaceInvCoeff.CFy[iMarker_Monitoring] += InvCoeff.CFy[iMarker];
2036 SurfaceInvCoeff.CFz[iMarker_Monitoring] += InvCoeff.CFz[iMarker];
2037 SurfaceInvCoeff.CMx[iMarker_Monitoring] += InvCoeff.CMx[iMarker];
2038 SurfaceInvCoeff.CMy[iMarker_Monitoring] += InvCoeff.CMy[iMarker];
2039 SurfaceInvCoeff.CMz[iMarker_Monitoring] += InvCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2040 }
2041 }
2042
2043 }
2044
2045 /*--- At the Nearfield SU2 only cares about the pressure coeffient ---*/
2046
2047 else {
2048 CNearFieldOF_Inv[iMarker] = NFPressOF;
2049 AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv += CNearFieldOF_Inv[iMarker];
2050 }
2051 }
2052 }
2053 }
2054
2055#ifdef HAVE_MPI
2056
2057 /*--- Add AllBound information using all the nodes ---*/
2058
2059 if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
2060 auto Allreduce = [](su2double x) {
2061 su2double tmp = x;
2062 x = 0.0;
2063 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&tmp, &x, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2064 return x;
2065 };
2066 AllBoundInvCoeff.CD = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CD);
2067 AllBoundInvCoeff.CL = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CL);
2068 AllBoundInvCoeff.CSF = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CSF);
2069 AllBoundInvCoeff.CEff = AllBoundInvCoeff.CL / (AllBoundInvCoeff.CD + EPS);
2070
2071 AllBoundInvCoeff.CMx = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CMx);
2072 AllBoundInvCoeff.CMy = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CMy);
2073 AllBoundInvCoeff.CMz = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CMz);
2074
2075 AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPx = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPx);
2076 AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPy = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPy);
2077 AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPz = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPz);
2078
2079 AllBoundInvCoeff.CFx = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CFx);
2080 AllBoundInvCoeff.CFy = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CFy);
2081 AllBoundInvCoeff.CFz = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CFz);
2082
2083 AllBoundInvCoeff.CT = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CT);
2084 AllBoundInvCoeff.CQ = Allreduce(AllBoundInvCoeff.CQ);
2085 AllBoundInvCoeff.CMerit = AllBoundInvCoeff.CT / (AllBoundInvCoeff.CQ + EPS);
2086 AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv = Allreduce(AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv);
2087 }
2088
2089 /*--- Add the forces on the surfaces using all the nodes ---*/
2090
2091 if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
2092 int nMarkerMon = config->GetnMarker_Monitoring();
2093
2094 /*--- Use the same buffer for all reductions. We could avoid the copy back into
2095 * the original variable by swaping pointers, but it is safer this way... ---*/
2096
2097 su2double* buffer = new su2double[nMarkerMon];
2098
2099 auto Allreduce_inplace = [buffer](int size, su2double* x) {
2100 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(x, buffer, size, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2101 for (int i = 0; i < size; ++i) x[i] = buffer[i];
2102 };
2103
2104 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceInvCoeff.CL);
2105 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceInvCoeff.CD);
2106 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceInvCoeff.CSF);
2107
2108 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < nMarkerMon; iMarker_Monitoring++)
2109 SurfaceInvCoeff.CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] =
2110 SurfaceInvCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] / (SurfaceInvCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
2111
2112 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceInvCoeff.CFx);
2113 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceInvCoeff.CFy);
2114 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceInvCoeff.CFz);
2115
2116 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceInvCoeff.CMx);
2117 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceInvCoeff.CMy);
2118 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceInvCoeff.CMz);
2119
2120 delete[] buffer;
2121 }
2122
2123#endif
2124
2125 /*--- Update the total coefficients (note that all the nodes have the same value) ---*/
2126
2127 TotalCoeff.CD = AllBoundInvCoeff.CD;
2128 TotalCoeff.CL = AllBoundInvCoeff.CL;
2129 TotalCoeff.CSF = AllBoundInvCoeff.CSF;
2130 TotalCoeff.CEff = TotalCoeff.CL / (TotalCoeff.CD + EPS);
2131 TotalCoeff.CFx = AllBoundInvCoeff.CFx;
2132 TotalCoeff.CFy = AllBoundInvCoeff.CFy;
2133 TotalCoeff.CFz = AllBoundInvCoeff.CFz;
2134 TotalCoeff.CMx = AllBoundInvCoeff.CMx;
2135 TotalCoeff.CMy = AllBoundInvCoeff.CMy;
2136 TotalCoeff.CMz = AllBoundInvCoeff.CMz;
2137 TotalCoeff.CoPx = AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPx;
2138 TotalCoeff.CoPy = AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPy;
2139 TotalCoeff.CoPz = AllBoundInvCoeff.CoPz;
2140 TotalCoeff.CT = AllBoundInvCoeff.CT;
2141 TotalCoeff.CQ = AllBoundInvCoeff.CQ;
2142 TotalCoeff.CMerit = TotalCoeff.CT / (TotalCoeff.CQ + EPS);
2143 Total_CNearFieldOF = AllBound_CNearFieldOF_Inv;
2144
2145 /*--- Update the total coefficients per surface (note that all the nodes have the same value)---*/
2146
2147 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
2148 SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceInvCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring];
2149 SurfaceCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceInvCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring];
2150 SurfaceCoeff.CSF[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceInvCoeff.CSF[iMarker_Monitoring];
2151 SurfaceCoeff.CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] =
2152 SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] / (SurfaceCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
2153 SurfaceCoeff.CFx[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceInvCoeff.CFx[iMarker_Monitoring];
2154 SurfaceCoeff.CFy[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceInvCoeff.CFy[iMarker_Monitoring];
2155 SurfaceCoeff.CFz[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceInvCoeff.CFz[iMarker_Monitoring];
2156 SurfaceCoeff.CMx[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceInvCoeff.CMx[iMarker_Monitoring];
2157 SurfaceCoeff.CMy[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceInvCoeff.CMy[iMarker_Monitoring];
2158 SurfaceCoeff.CMz[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceInvCoeff.CMz[iMarker_Monitoring];
2159 }
2160}
2161
2162template <class V, ENUM_REGIME FlowRegime>
2163void CFVMFlowSolverBase<V, FlowRegime>::Momentum_Forces(const CGeometry* geometry, const CConfig* config) {
2164 unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
2165 unsigned short iDim, iMarker, Boundary, Monitoring, iMarker_Monitoring;
2166 su2double MassFlow, Density;
2167 const su2double *Normal = nullptr, *Coord = nullptr;
2168 string Marker_Tag, Monitoring_Tag;
2169 su2double AxiFactor;
2170
2171 su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA() * PI_NUMBER / 180.0;
2172 su2double Beta = config->GetAoS() * PI_NUMBER / 180.0;
2173 su2double RefLength = config->GetRefLength();
2174 auto Origin = config->GetRefOriginMoment(0);
2175 bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
2176
2177 const su2double factor = 1.0 / AeroCoeffForceRef;
2178
2179 /*-- Variables initialization ---*/
2180
2181 AllBoundMntCoeff.setZero();
2182 SurfaceMntCoeff.setZero();
2183
2184 /*--- Loop over the Inlet -Outlet Markers ---*/
2185
2186 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
2187 Boundary = config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker);
2188 Monitoring = config->GetMarker_All_Monitoring(iMarker);
2189
2190 /*--- Obtain the origin for the moment computation for a particular marker ---*/
2191
2192 if (Monitoring == YES) {
2193 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
2194 Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring_TagBound(iMarker_Monitoring);
2195 Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
2196 if (Marker_Tag == Monitoring_Tag) Origin = config->GetRefOriginMoment(iMarker_Monitoring);
2197 }
2198 }
2199
2200 if ((Boundary == INLET_FLOW) || (Boundary == OUTLET_FLOW) || (Boundary == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
2201 (Boundary == ACTDISK_OUTLET) || (Boundary == ENGINE_INFLOW) || (Boundary == ENGINE_EXHAUST)) {
2202 /*--- Forces initialization at each Marker ---*/
2203
2204 MntCoeff.setZero(iMarker);
2205
2206 su2double ForceMomentum[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, MomentMomentum[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
2207 su2double MomentX_Force[3] = {0.0}, MomentY_Force[3] = {0.0}, MomentZ_Force[3] = {0.0};
2208
2209 /*--- Loop over the vertices to compute the forces ---*/
2210
2211 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
2212 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2213
2214 /*--- Note that the pressure coefficient is computed at the
2215 halo cells (for visualization purposes), but not the forces ---*/
2216
2217 if ((geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) && (Monitoring == YES)) {
2218 Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
2219 Coord = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
2220 Density = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
2221 MassFlow = 0.0;
2222 su2double Velocity[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, MomentDist[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
2223 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2224 Velocity[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint, iDim);
2225 MomentDist[iDim] = Coord[iDim] - Origin[iDim];
2226 MassFlow -= Normal[iDim] * Velocity[iDim] * Density;
2227 }
2228
2229 /*--- Axisymmetric simulations ---*/
2230
2231 if (axisymmetric)
2232 AxiFactor = 2.0 * PI_NUMBER * geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1);
2233 else
2234 AxiFactor = 1.0;
2235
2236 /*--- Force computation, note the minus sign due to the
2237 orientation of the normal (outward) ---*/
2238
2239 su2double Force[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
2240 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2241 Force[iDim] = MassFlow * Velocity[iDim] * factor * AxiFactor;
2242 ForceMomentum[iDim] += Force[iDim];
2243 }
2244
2245 /*--- Moment with respect to the reference axis ---*/
2246
2247 if (nDim == 3) {
2248 MomentMomentum[0] += (Force[2] * MomentDist[1] - Force[1] * MomentDist[2]) / RefLength;
2249 MomentX_Force[1] += (-Force[1] * Coord[2]);
2250 MomentX_Force[2] += (Force[2] * Coord[1]);
2251
2252 MomentMomentum[1] += (Force[0] * MomentDist[2] - Force[2] * MomentDist[0]) / RefLength;
2253 MomentY_Force[2] += (-Force[2] * Coord[0]);
2254 MomentY_Force[0] += (Force[0] * Coord[2]);
2255 }
2256 MomentMomentum[2] += (Force[1] * MomentDist[0] - Force[0] * MomentDist[1]) / RefLength;
2257 MomentZ_Force[0] += (-Force[0] * Coord[1]);
2258 MomentZ_Force[1] += (Force[1] * Coord[0]);
2259 }
2260 }
2261
2262 /*--- Project forces and store the non-dimensional coefficients ---*/
2263
2264 if (Monitoring == YES) {
2265 if (nDim == 2) {
2266 MntCoeff.CD[iMarker] = ForceMomentum[0] * cos(Alpha) + ForceMomentum[1] * sin(Alpha);
2267 MntCoeff.CL[iMarker] = -ForceMomentum[0] * sin(Alpha) + ForceMomentum[1] * cos(Alpha);
2268 MntCoeff.CEff[iMarker] = MntCoeff.CL[iMarker] / (MntCoeff.CD[iMarker] + EPS);
2269 MntCoeff.CFx[iMarker] = ForceMomentum[0];
2270 MntCoeff.CFy[iMarker] = ForceMomentum[1];
2271 MntCoeff.CMz[iMarker] = MomentMomentum[2];
2272 MntCoeff.CoPx[iMarker] = MomentZ_Force[1];
2273 MntCoeff.CoPy[iMarker] = -MomentZ_Force[0];
2274 MntCoeff.CT[iMarker] = -MntCoeff.CFx[iMarker];
2275 MntCoeff.CQ[iMarker] = -MntCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2276 MntCoeff.CMerit[iMarker] = MntCoeff.CT[iMarker] / (MntCoeff.CQ[iMarker] + EPS);
2277 }
2278 if (nDim == 3) {
2279 MntCoeff.CD[iMarker] = ForceMomentum[0] * cos(Alpha) * cos(Beta) + ForceMomentum[1] * sin(Beta) +
2280 ForceMomentum[2] * sin(Alpha) * cos(Beta);
2281 MntCoeff.CL[iMarker] = -ForceMomentum[0] * sin(Alpha) + ForceMomentum[2] * cos(Alpha);
2282 MntCoeff.CSF[iMarker] = -ForceMomentum[0] * sin(Beta) * cos(Alpha) + ForceMomentum[1] * cos(Beta) -
2283 ForceMomentum[2] * sin(Beta) * sin(Alpha);
2284 MntCoeff.CEff[iMarker] = MntCoeff.CL[iMarker] / (MntCoeff.CD[iMarker] + EPS);
2285 MntCoeff.CFx[iMarker] = ForceMomentum[0];
2286 MntCoeff.CFy[iMarker] = ForceMomentum[1];
2287 MntCoeff.CFz[iMarker] = ForceMomentum[2];
2288 MntCoeff.CMx[iMarker] = MomentMomentum[0];
2289 MntCoeff.CMy[iMarker] = MomentMomentum[1];
2290 MntCoeff.CMz[iMarker] = MomentMomentum[2];
2291 MntCoeff.CoPx[iMarker] = -MomentY_Force[0];
2292 MntCoeff.CoPz[iMarker] = MomentY_Force[2];
2293 MntCoeff.CT[iMarker] = -MntCoeff.CFz[iMarker];
2294 MntCoeff.CQ[iMarker] = -MntCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2295 MntCoeff.CMerit[iMarker] = MntCoeff.CT[iMarker] / (MntCoeff.CQ[iMarker] + EPS);
2296 }
2297
2298 AllBoundMntCoeff.CD += MntCoeff.CD[iMarker];
2299 AllBoundMntCoeff.CL += MntCoeff.CL[iMarker];
2300 AllBoundMntCoeff.CSF += MntCoeff.CSF[iMarker];
2301 AllBoundMntCoeff.CEff = AllBoundMntCoeff.CL / (AllBoundMntCoeff.CD + EPS);
2302 AllBoundMntCoeff.CFx += MntCoeff.CFx[iMarker];
2303 AllBoundMntCoeff.CFy += MntCoeff.CFy[iMarker];
2304 AllBoundMntCoeff.CFz += MntCoeff.CFz[iMarker];
2305 AllBoundMntCoeff.CMx += MntCoeff.CMx[iMarker];
2306 AllBoundMntCoeff.CMy += MntCoeff.CMy[iMarker];
2307 AllBoundMntCoeff.CMx += MntCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2308 AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPx += MntCoeff.CoPx[iMarker];
2309 AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPy += MntCoeff.CoPy[iMarker];
2310 AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPz += MntCoeff.CoPz[iMarker];
2311 AllBoundMntCoeff.CT += MntCoeff.CT[iMarker];
2312 AllBoundMntCoeff.CQ += MntCoeff.CQ[iMarker];
2313 AllBoundMntCoeff.CMerit += AllBoundMntCoeff.CT / (AllBoundMntCoeff.CQ + EPS);
2314
2315 /*--- Compute the coefficients per surface ---*/
2316
2317 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
2318 Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring_TagBound(iMarker_Monitoring);
2319 Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
2320 if (Marker_Tag == Monitoring_Tag) {
2321 SurfaceMntCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] += MntCoeff.CL[iMarker];
2322 SurfaceMntCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] += MntCoeff.CD[iMarker];
2323 SurfaceMntCoeff.CSF[iMarker_Monitoring] += MntCoeff.CSF[iMarker];
2324 SurfaceMntCoeff.CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceMntCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] / (SurfaceMntCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
2325 SurfaceMntCoeff.CFx[iMarker_Monitoring] += MntCoeff.CFx[iMarker];
2326 SurfaceMntCoeff.CFy[iMarker_Monitoring] += MntCoeff.CFy[iMarker];
2327 SurfaceMntCoeff.CFz[iMarker_Monitoring] += MntCoeff.CFz[iMarker];
2328 SurfaceMntCoeff.CMx[iMarker_Monitoring] += MntCoeff.CMx[iMarker];
2329 SurfaceMntCoeff.CMy[iMarker_Monitoring] += MntCoeff.CMy[iMarker];
2330 SurfaceMntCoeff.CMz[iMarker_Monitoring] += MntCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2331 }
2332 }
2333 }
2334 }
2335 }
2336
2337#ifdef HAVE_MPI
2338
2339 /*--- Add AllBound information using all the nodes ---*/
2340
2341 if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
2342 auto Allreduce = [](su2double x) {
2343 su2double tmp = x;
2344 x = 0.0;
2345 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&tmp, &x, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2346 return x;
2347 };
2348
2349 AllBoundMntCoeff.CD = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CD);
2350 AllBoundMntCoeff.CL = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CL);
2351 AllBoundMntCoeff.CSF = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CSF);
2352 AllBoundMntCoeff.CEff = AllBoundMntCoeff.CL / (AllBoundMntCoeff.CD + EPS);
2353
2354 AllBoundMntCoeff.CFx = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CFx);
2355 AllBoundMntCoeff.CFy = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CFy);
2356 AllBoundMntCoeff.CFz = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CFz);
2357
2358 AllBoundMntCoeff.CMx = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CMx);
2359 AllBoundMntCoeff.CMy = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CMy);
2360 AllBoundMntCoeff.CMz = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CMz);
2361
2362 AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPx = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPx);
2363 AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPy = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPy);
2364 AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPz = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPz);
2365
2366 AllBoundMntCoeff.CT = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CT);
2367 AllBoundMntCoeff.CQ = Allreduce(AllBoundMntCoeff.CQ);
2368 AllBoundMntCoeff.CMerit = AllBoundMntCoeff.CT / (AllBoundMntCoeff.CQ + EPS);
2369 }
2370
2371 /*--- Add the forces on the surfaces using all the nodes ---*/
2372
2373 if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
2374 int nMarkerMon = config->GetnMarker_Monitoring();
2375
2376 /*--- Use the same buffer for all reductions. We could avoid the copy back into
2377 * the original variable by swaping pointers, but it is safer this way... ---*/
2378
2379 su2double* buffer = new su2double[nMarkerMon];
2380
2381 auto Allreduce_inplace = [buffer](int size, su2double* x) {
2382 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(x, buffer, size, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2383 for (int i = 0; i < size; ++i) x[i] = buffer[i];
2384 };
2385
2386 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceMntCoeff.CL);
2387 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceMntCoeff.CD);
2388 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceMntCoeff.CSF);
2389
2390 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < nMarkerMon; iMarker_Monitoring++)
2391 SurfaceMntCoeff.CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] =
2392 SurfaceMntCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] / (SurfaceMntCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
2393
2394 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceMntCoeff.CFx);
2395 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceMntCoeff.CFy);
2396 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceMntCoeff.CFz);
2397
2398 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceMntCoeff.CMx);
2399 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceMntCoeff.CMy);
2400 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceMntCoeff.CMz);
2401
2402 delete[] buffer;
2403 }
2404
2405#endif
2406
2407 /*--- Update the total coefficients (note that all the nodes have the same value) ---*/
2408
2409 TotalCoeff.CD += AllBoundMntCoeff.CD;
2410 TotalCoeff.CL += AllBoundMntCoeff.CL;
2411 TotalCoeff.CSF += AllBoundMntCoeff.CSF;
2412 TotalCoeff.CEff = TotalCoeff.CL / (TotalCoeff.CD + EPS);
2413 TotalCoeff.CFx += AllBoundMntCoeff.CFx;
2414 TotalCoeff.CFy += AllBoundMntCoeff.CFy;
2415 TotalCoeff.CFz += AllBoundMntCoeff.CFz;
2416 TotalCoeff.CMx += AllBoundMntCoeff.CMx;
2417 TotalCoeff.CMy += AllBoundMntCoeff.CMy;
2418 TotalCoeff.CMz += AllBoundMntCoeff.CMz;
2419 TotalCoeff.CoPx += AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPx;
2420 TotalCoeff.CoPy += AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPy;
2421 TotalCoeff.CoPz += AllBoundMntCoeff.CoPz;
2422 TotalCoeff.CT += AllBoundMntCoeff.CT;
2423 TotalCoeff.CQ += AllBoundMntCoeff.CQ;
2424 TotalCoeff.CMerit = TotalCoeff.CT / (TotalCoeff.CQ + EPS);
2425
2426 /*--- Update the total coefficients per surface (note that all the nodes have the same value)---*/
2427
2428 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
2429 SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceMntCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring];
2430 SurfaceCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceMntCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring];
2431 SurfaceCoeff.CSF[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceMntCoeff.CSF[iMarker_Monitoring];
2432 SurfaceCoeff.CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] =
2433 SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] / (SurfaceCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
2434 SurfaceCoeff.CFx[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceMntCoeff.CFx[iMarker_Monitoring];
2435 SurfaceCoeff.CFy[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceMntCoeff.CFy[iMarker_Monitoring];
2436 SurfaceCoeff.CFz[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceMntCoeff.CFz[iMarker_Monitoring];
2437 SurfaceCoeff.CMx[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceMntCoeff.CMx[iMarker_Monitoring];
2438 SurfaceCoeff.CMy[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceMntCoeff.CMy[iMarker_Monitoring];
2439 SurfaceCoeff.CMz[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceMntCoeff.CMz[iMarker_Monitoring];
2440 }

2443template <class V, ENUM_REGIME FlowRegime>
2444void CFVMFlowSolverBase<V, FlowRegime>::Friction_Forces(const CGeometry* geometry, const CConfig* config) {
2445 /// TODO: Major cleanup needed.
2446
2447 if (!config->GetViscous()) return;
2448
2449 unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, iPointNormal;
2450 unsigned short iMarker, iMarker_Monitoring, iDim, jDim;
2451 su2double Viscosity = 0.0, Area, Density = 0.0, WallDistMod, FrictionVel,
2452 UnitNormal[3] = {0.0}, TauElem[3] = {0.0}, Tau[3][3] = {{0.0}}, Cp,
2453 thermal_conductivity, MaxNorm = 8.0, Grad_Vel[3][3] = {{0.0}}, Grad_Temp[3] = {0.0},
2454 Grad_Temp_ve[3] = {0.0}, AxiFactor;
2455 const su2double *Coord = nullptr, *Coord_Normal = nullptr, *Normal = nullptr;
2456 const su2double minYPlus = config->GetwallModel_MinYPlus();
2457
2458 string Marker_Tag, Monitoring_Tag;
2459
2460 const su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA() * PI_NUMBER / 180.0;
2461 const su2double Beta = config->GetAoS() * PI_NUMBER / 180.0;
2462 const su2double RefLength = config->GetRefLength();
2463 const su2double RefHeatFlux = config->GetHeat_Flux_Ref();
2464 const su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
2465 auto Origin = config->GetRefOriginMoment(0);
2466
2467 const su2double Prandtl_Lam = config->GetPrandtl_Lam();
2468 const bool energy = config->GetEnergy_Equation();
2469 const bool QCR = config->GetSAParsedOptions().qcr2000;
2470 const bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
2471 const bool roughwall = (config->GetnRoughWall() > 0);
2472 const bool nemo = config->GetNEMOProblem();
2473
2474 const su2double factor = 1.0 / AeroCoeffForceRef;
2475 const su2double factorFric = config->GetRefArea() * factor;
2476
2477 /*--- Variables initialization ---*/
2478
2479 AllBoundViscCoeff.setZero();
2480 SurfaceViscCoeff.setZero();
2481
2482 AllBound_HF_Visc = 0.0;
2483 AllBound_MaxHF_Visc = 0.0;
2484
2485 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
2486 Surface_HF_Visc[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
2487 Surface_MaxHF_Visc[iMarker_Monitoring] = 0.0;
2488 }
2489
2490 /*--- Loop over the Navier-Stokes markers ---*/
2491
2492 for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
2493
2494 Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
2495 if (!config->GetViscous_Wall(iMarker)) continue;
2496
2497 /*--- Obtain the origin for the moment computation for a particular marker ---*/
2498
2499 const auto Monitoring = config->GetMarker_All_Monitoring(iMarker);
2500 if (Monitoring == YES) {
2501 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
2502 Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring_TagBound(iMarker_Monitoring);
2503 if (Marker_Tag == Monitoring_Tag) Origin = config->GetRefOriginMoment(iMarker_Monitoring);
2504 }
2505 }
2506
2507 /*--- Forces initialization at each Marker ---*/
2508
2509 ViscCoeff.setZero(iMarker);
2510
2511 HF_Visc[iMarker] = 0.0;
2512 MaxHF_Visc[iMarker] = 0.0;
2513
2514 su2double ForceViscous[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, MomentViscous[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
2515 su2double MomentX_Force[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, MomentY_Force[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, MomentZ_Force[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
2516
2517 /* --- check if wall functions are used --- */
2518
2519 const bool wallfunctions = (config->GetWallFunction_Treatment(Marker_Tag) != WALL_FUNCTIONS::NONE);
2520
2521 /*--- Loop over the vertices to compute the forces ---*/
2522
2523 for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
2524 iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2525
2526 Coord = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
2527
2528 Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
2529
2530 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2531 for (jDim = 0; jDim < nDim; jDim++) {
2532 Grad_Vel[iDim][jDim] = nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint, prim_idx.Velocity() + iDim, jDim);
2533 }
2534 Grad_Temp[iDim] = nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint, prim_idx.Temperature(), iDim);
2535 if (nemo) Grad_Temp_ve[iDim] = nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint, prim_idx.Temperature_ve(), iDim);
2536 }
2537
2538 Viscosity = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
2539 if (roughwall) {
2540 WALL_TYPE WallType;
2541 su2double Roughness_Height;
2542 tie(WallType, Roughness_Height) = config->GetWallRoughnessProperties(Marker_Tag);
2543 if (WallType == WALL_TYPE::ROUGH) Viscosity += nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
2544 }
2545 Density = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
2546
2547 Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
2548 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2549 UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim] / Area;
2550 }
2551
2552 /*--- Evaluate Tau ---*/
2553 CNumerics::ComputeStressTensor(nDim, Tau, Grad_Vel, Viscosity);
2554
2555 /*--- If necessary evaluate the QCR contribution to Tau ---*/
2556
2557 if (QCR) CNumerics::AddQCR(nDim, Grad_Vel, Tau);
2558
2559 /*--- Project Tau in each surface element ---*/
2560
2561 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2562 TauElem[iDim] = 0.0;
2563 for (jDim = 0; jDim < nDim; jDim++) {
2564 TauElem[iDim] += Tau[iDim][jDim] * UnitNormal[jDim];
2565 }
2566 }
2567
2568 /*--- Compute wall shear stress (using the stress tensor). Compute wall skin friction coefficient, and heat flux
2569 * on the wall ---*/
2570
2571 su2double TauTangent[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
2572 GeometryToolbox::TangentProjection(nDim, Tau, UnitNormal, TauTangent);
2573
2574 WallShearStress[iMarker][iVertex] = GeometryToolbox::Norm(int(MAXNDIM), TauTangent);
2575
2576 /*--- For wall functions, the wall stresses need to be scaled by the wallfunction stress Tau_Wall---*/
2577 su2double Tau_Wall, scale;
2578 if (wallfunctions && (YPlus[iMarker][iVertex] > minYPlus)){
2579 Tau_Wall = nodes->GetTau_Wall(iPoint);
2580 scale = Tau_Wall / WallShearStress[iMarker][iVertex];
2581 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2582 TauTangent[iDim] *= scale;
2583 TauElem[iDim] *= scale;
2584 }
2585
2586 WallShearStress[iMarker][iVertex] = Tau_Wall;
2587 }
2588
2589 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2590 CSkinFriction[iMarker](iVertex,iDim) = TauTangent[iDim] * factorFric;
2591 }
2592
2593 /*--- Compute non-dimensional velocity and y+ ---*/
2594
2595 FrictionVel = sqrt(fabs(WallShearStress[iMarker][iVertex]) / Density);
2596
2597 if (!wallfunctions && (MGLevel == MESH_0 || geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint))) {
2598 // for CMultiGridGeometry, the normal neighbor of halo nodes in not set
2599 iPointNormal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
2600 Coord_Normal = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPointNormal);
2601 WallDistMod = GeometryToolbox::Distance(nDim, Coord, Coord_Normal);
2602 YPlus[iMarker][iVertex] = WallDistMod * FrictionVel / (Viscosity / Density);
2603 }
2604
2605 /*--- Compute total and maximum heat flux on the wall ---*/
2606
2607 su2double dTdn = -GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(nDim, Grad_Temp, UnitNormal);
2608
2609 if (!nemo){
2610
2611 if (FlowRegime == ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE) {
2612
2613 Cp = (Gamma / Gamma_Minus_One) * Gas_Constant;
2614 thermal_conductivity = Cp * Viscosity / Prandtl_Lam;
2615 }
2616 if (FlowRegime == ENUM_REGIME::INCOMPRESSIBLE) {
2617 if (!energy) dTdn = 0.0;
2618 thermal_conductivity = nodes->GetThermalConductivity(iPoint);
2619 }
2620 HeatFlux[iMarker][iVertex] = -thermal_conductivity * dTdn * RefHeatFlux;
2621
2622 } else {
2623
2624 const auto& thermal_conductivity_tr = nodes->GetThermalConductivity(iPoint);
2625 const auto& thermal_conductivity_ve = nodes->GetThermalConductivity_ve(iPoint);
2626
2627 const su2double dTvedn = -GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(nDim, Grad_Temp_ve, UnitNormal);
2628
2629 /*--- Surface energy balance: trans-rot heat flux, vib-el heat flux ---*/
2630 HeatFlux[iMarker][iVertex] = -(thermal_conductivity_tr*dTdn + thermal_conductivity_ve*dTvedn);
2631
2632 /*--- Compute enthalpy transport to surface due to mass diffusion ---*/
2633 bool catalytic = config->GetCatalytic_Wall(iMarker);
2634 if (catalytic){
2635
2636 const auto nSpecies = config->GetnSpecies();
2637 const auto& Grad_PrimVar = nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint);
2638 const auto& PrimVar = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
2639 const auto& Ds = nodes->GetDiffusionCoeff(iPoint);
2640 const auto& hs = nodes->GetEnthalpys(iPoint);
2641 const su2double rho = PrimVar[prim_idx.Density()];
2642
2643 su2double sumJhs = 0.0;
2644 for (auto iSpecies = 0u; iSpecies < nSpecies; iSpecies++) {
2645 for (auto iDim = 0u; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2646 su2double dYdn = 1.0/rho*(Grad_PrimVar[iSpecies][iDim] - PrimVar[iSpecies]*Grad_PrimVar[prim_idx.Density()][iDim]/rho);
2647 sumJhs += rho*Ds[iSpecies]*hs[iSpecies]*dYdn*UnitNormal[iDim];
2648 }
2649 }
2650 /*--- Surface energy balance: mass diffusion ---*/
2651 HeatFlux[iMarker][iVertex] += sumJhs;
2652
2653 }
2654 }
2655
2656 /*--- Note that heat is computed at the
2657 halo cells (for visualization purposes), but not the forces ---*/
2658
2659 if ((geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) && (Monitoring == YES)) {
2660 /*--- Axisymmetric simulations ---*/
2661
2662 if (axisymmetric)
2663 AxiFactor = 2.0 * PI_NUMBER * geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1);
2664 else
2665 AxiFactor = 1.0;
2666
2667 /*--- Force computation ---*/
2668
2669 su2double Force[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, MomentDist[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
2670 for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2671 Force[iDim] = TauElem[iDim] * Area * factor * AxiFactor;
2672 ForceViscous[iDim] += Force[iDim];
2673 MomentDist[iDim] = Coord[iDim] - Origin[iDim];
2674 }
2675
2676 /*--- Moment with respect to the reference axis ---*/
2677
2678 if (nDim == 3) {
2679 MomentViscous[0] += (Force[2] * MomentDist[1] - Force[1] * MomentDist[2]) / RefLength;
2680 MomentX_Force[1] += (-Force[1] * Coord[2]);
2681 MomentX_Force[2] += (Force[2] * Coord[1]);
2682
2683 MomentViscous[1] += (Force[0] * MomentDist[2] - Force[2] * MomentDist[0]) / RefLength;
2684 MomentY_Force[2] += (-Force[2] * Coord[0]);
2685 MomentY_Force[0] += (Force[0] * Coord[2]);
2686 }
2687 MomentViscous[2] += (Force[1] * MomentDist[0] - Force[0] * MomentDist[1]) / RefLength;
2688 MomentZ_Force[0] += (-Force[0] * Coord[1]);
2689 MomentZ_Force[1] += (Force[1] * Coord[0]);
2690
2691 HF_Visc[iMarker] += HeatFlux[iMarker][iVertex] * Area;
2692 MaxHF_Visc[iMarker] += pow(HeatFlux[iMarker][iVertex], MaxNorm);
2693 }
2694 }
2695
2696 /*--- Project forces and store the non-dimensional coefficients ---*/
2697
2698 if (Monitoring == YES) {
2699 if (nDim == 2) {
2700 ViscCoeff.CD[iMarker] = ForceViscous[0] * cos(Alpha) + ForceViscous[1] * sin(Alpha);
2701 ViscCoeff.CL[iMarker] = -ForceViscous[0] * sin(Alpha) + ForceViscous[1] * cos(Alpha);
2702 ViscCoeff.CEff[iMarker] = ViscCoeff.CL[iMarker] / (ViscCoeff.CD[iMarker] + EPS);
2703 ViscCoeff.CFx[iMarker] = ForceViscous[0];
2704 ViscCoeff.CFy[iMarker] = ForceViscous[1];
2705 ViscCoeff.CMz[iMarker] = MomentViscous[2];
2706 ViscCoeff.CoPx[iMarker] = MomentZ_Force[1];
2707 ViscCoeff.CoPy[iMarker] = -MomentZ_Force[0];
2708 ViscCoeff.CT[iMarker] = -ViscCoeff.CFx[iMarker];
2709 ViscCoeff.CQ[iMarker] = -ViscCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2710 ViscCoeff.CMerit[iMarker] = ViscCoeff.CT[iMarker] / (ViscCoeff.CQ[iMarker] + EPS);
2711 MaxHF_Visc[iMarker] = pow(MaxHF_Visc[iMarker], 1.0 / MaxNorm);
2712 }
2713 if (nDim == 3) {
2714 ViscCoeff.CD[iMarker] = ForceViscous[0] * cos(Alpha) * cos(Beta) + ForceViscous[1] * sin(Beta) +
2715 ForceViscous[2] * sin(Alpha) * cos(Beta);
2716 ViscCoeff.CL[iMarker] = -ForceViscous[0] * sin(Alpha) + ForceViscous[2] * cos(Alpha);
2717 ViscCoeff.CSF[iMarker] = -ForceViscous[0] * sin(Beta) * cos(Alpha) + ForceViscous[1] * cos(Beta) -
2718 ForceViscous[2] * sin(Beta) * sin(Alpha);
2719 ViscCoeff.CEff[iMarker] = ViscCoeff.CL[iMarker] / (ViscCoeff.CD[iMarker] + EPS);
2720 ViscCoeff.CFx[iMarker] = ForceViscous[0];
2721 ViscCoeff.CFy[iMarker] = ForceViscous[1];
2722 ViscCoeff.CFz[iMarker] = ForceViscous[2];
2723 ViscCoeff.CMx[iMarker] = MomentViscous[0];
2724 ViscCoeff.CMy[iMarker] = MomentViscous[1];
2725 ViscCoeff.CMz[iMarker] = MomentViscous[2];
2726 ViscCoeff.CoPx[iMarker] = -MomentY_Force[0];
2727 ViscCoeff.CoPz[iMarker] = MomentY_Force[2];
2728 ViscCoeff.CT[iMarker] = -ViscCoeff.CFz[iMarker];
2729 ViscCoeff.CQ[iMarker] = -ViscCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2730 ViscCoeff.CMerit[iMarker] = ViscCoeff.CT[iMarker] / (ViscCoeff.CQ[iMarker] + EPS);
2731 MaxHF_Visc[iMarker] = pow(MaxHF_Visc[iMarker], 1.0 / MaxNorm);
2732 }
2733
2734 AllBoundViscCoeff.CD += ViscCoeff.CD[iMarker];
2735 AllBoundViscCoeff.CL += ViscCoeff.CL[iMarker];
2736 AllBoundViscCoeff.CSF += ViscCoeff.CSF[iMarker];
2737 AllBoundViscCoeff.CFx += ViscCoeff.CFx[iMarker];
2738 AllBoundViscCoeff.CFy += ViscCoeff.CFy[iMarker];
2739 AllBoundViscCoeff.CFz += ViscCoeff.CFz[iMarker];
2740 AllBoundViscCoeff.CMx += ViscCoeff.CMx[iMarker];
2741 AllBoundViscCoeff.CMy += ViscCoeff.CMy[iMarker];
2742 AllBoundViscCoeff.CMz += ViscCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2743 AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPx += ViscCoeff.CoPx[iMarker];
2744 AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPy += ViscCoeff.CoPy[iMarker];
2745 AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPz += ViscCoeff.CoPz[iMarker];
2746 AllBoundViscCoeff.CT += ViscCoeff.CT[iMarker];
2747 AllBoundViscCoeff.CQ += ViscCoeff.CQ[iMarker];
2748 AllBound_HF_Visc += HF_Visc[iMarker];
2749 AllBound_MaxHF_Visc += pow(MaxHF_Visc[iMarker], MaxNorm);
2750
2751 /*--- Compute the coefficients per surface ---*/
2752
2753 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
2754 Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring_TagBound(iMarker_Monitoring);
2755 Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
2756 if (Marker_Tag == Monitoring_Tag) {
2757 SurfaceViscCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] += ViscCoeff.CL[iMarker];
2758 SurfaceViscCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] += ViscCoeff.CD[iMarker];
2759 SurfaceViscCoeff.CSF[iMarker_Monitoring] += ViscCoeff.CSF[iMarker];
2760 SurfaceViscCoeff.CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] = SurfaceViscCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] / (SurfaceViscCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
2761 SurfaceViscCoeff.CFx[iMarker_Monitoring] += ViscCoeff.CFx[iMarker];
2762 SurfaceViscCoeff.CFy[iMarker_Monitoring] += ViscCoeff.CFy[iMarker];
2763 SurfaceViscCoeff.CFz[iMarker_Monitoring] += ViscCoeff.CFz[iMarker];
2764 SurfaceViscCoeff.CMx[iMarker_Monitoring] += ViscCoeff.CMx[iMarker];
2765 SurfaceViscCoeff.CMy[iMarker_Monitoring] += ViscCoeff.CMy[iMarker];
2766 SurfaceViscCoeff.CMz[iMarker_Monitoring] += ViscCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2767 Surface_HF_Visc[iMarker_Monitoring] += HF_Visc[iMarker];
2768 Surface_MaxHF_Visc[iMarker_Monitoring] += pow(MaxHF_Visc[iMarker], MaxNorm);
2769 }
2770 }
2771 }
2772 }
2773
2774 /*--- Update some global coeffients ---*/
2775
2776 AllBoundViscCoeff.CEff = AllBoundViscCoeff.CL / (AllBoundViscCoeff.CD + EPS);
2777 AllBoundViscCoeff.CMerit = AllBoundViscCoeff.CT / (AllBoundViscCoeff.CQ + EPS);
2778
2779#ifdef HAVE_MPI
2780
2781 /*--- Add AllBound information using all the nodes ---*/
2782
2783 if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
2784 auto Allreduce = [](su2double x) {
2785 su2double tmp = x;
2786 x = 0.0;
2787 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&tmp, &x, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2788 return x;
2789 };
2790 AllBoundViscCoeff.CD = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CD);
2791 AllBoundViscCoeff.CL = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CL);
2792 AllBoundViscCoeff.CSF = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CSF);
2793 AllBoundViscCoeff.CEff = AllBoundViscCoeff.CL / (AllBoundViscCoeff.CD + EPS);
2794
2795 AllBoundViscCoeff.CMx = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CMx);
2796 AllBoundViscCoeff.CMy = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CMy);
2797 AllBoundViscCoeff.CMz = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CMz);
2798
2799 AllBoundViscCoeff.CFx = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CFx);
2800 AllBoundViscCoeff.CFy = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CFy);
2801 AllBoundViscCoeff.CFz = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CFz);
2802
2803 AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPx = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPx);
2804 AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPy = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPy);
2805 AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPz = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPz);
2806
2807 AllBoundViscCoeff.CT = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CT);
2808 AllBoundViscCoeff.CQ = Allreduce(AllBoundViscCoeff.CQ);
2809 AllBoundViscCoeff.CMerit = AllBoundViscCoeff.CT / (AllBoundViscCoeff.CQ + EPS);
2810
2811 AllBound_HF_Visc = Allreduce(AllBound_HF_Visc);
2812 AllBound_MaxHF_Visc = Allreduce(AllBound_MaxHF_Visc);
2813 }
2814
2815 /*--- Add the forces on the surfaces using all the nodes ---*/
2816
2817 if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
2818 int nMarkerMon = config->GetnMarker_Monitoring();
2819
2820 /*--- Use the same buffer for all reductions. We could avoid the copy back into
2821 * the original variable by swaping pointers, but it is safer this way... ---*/
2822
2823 su2double* buffer = new su2double[nMarkerMon];
2824
2825 auto Allreduce_inplace = [buffer](int size, su2double* x) {
2826 SU2_MPI::Allreduce(x, buffer, size, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2827 for (int i = 0; i < size; ++i) x[i] = buffer[i];
2828 };
2829
2830 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceViscCoeff.CL);
2831 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceViscCoeff.CD);
2832 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceViscCoeff.CSF);
2833
2834 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < nMarkerMon; iMarker_Monitoring++)
2835 SurfaceViscCoeff.CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] =
2836 SurfaceViscCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] / (SurfaceViscCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
2837
2838 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceViscCoeff.CFx);
2839 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceViscCoeff.CFy);
2840 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceViscCoeff.CFz);
2841
2842 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceViscCoeff.CMx);
2843 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceViscCoeff.CMy);
2844 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, SurfaceViscCoeff.CMz);
2845
2846 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, Surface_HF_Visc.data());
2847 Allreduce_inplace(nMarkerMon, Surface_MaxHF_Visc.data());
2848
2849 delete[] buffer;
2850 }
2851
2852#endif
2853
2854 /*--- Complete the calculation of maximum heat flux. ---*/
2855
2856 for (auto& hf : Surface_MaxHF_Visc) {
2857 hf = pow(hf, 1.0 / MaxNorm);
2858 }
2859 AllBound_MaxHF_Visc = pow(AllBound_MaxHF_Visc, 1.0 / MaxNorm);
2860
2861 /*--- Update the total coefficients (note that all the nodes have the same value)---*/
2862
2863 TotalCoeff.CD += AllBoundViscCoeff.CD;
2864 TotalCoeff.CL += AllBoundViscCoeff.CL;
2865 TotalCoeff.CSF += AllBoundViscCoeff.CSF;
2866 TotalCoeff.CEff = TotalCoeff.CL / (TotalCoeff.CD + EPS);
2867 TotalCoeff.CFx += AllBoundViscCoeff.CFx;
2868 TotalCoeff.CFy += AllBoundViscCoeff.CFy;
2869 TotalCoeff.CFz += AllBoundViscCoeff.CFz;
2870 TotalCoeff.CMx += AllBoundViscCoeff.CMx;
2871 TotalCoeff.CMy += AllBoundViscCoeff.CMy;
2872 TotalCoeff.CMz += AllBoundViscCoeff.CMz;
2873 TotalCoeff.CoPx += AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPx;
2874 TotalCoeff.CoPy += AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPy;
2875 TotalCoeff.CoPz += AllBoundViscCoeff.CoPz;
2876 TotalCoeff.CT += AllBoundViscCoeff.CT;
2877 TotalCoeff.CQ += AllBoundViscCoeff.CQ;
2878 TotalCoeff.CMerit = AllBoundViscCoeff.CT / (AllBoundViscCoeff.CQ + EPS);
2879 Total_Heat = AllBound_HF_Visc;
2880 Total_MaxHeat = AllBound_MaxHF_Visc;
2881
2882 /*--- Update the total coefficients per surface (note that all the nodes have the same value)---*/
2883
2884 for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
2885 SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceViscCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring];
2886 SurfaceCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceViscCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring];
2887 SurfaceCoeff.CSF[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceViscCoeff.CSF[iMarker_Monitoring];
2888 SurfaceCoeff.CEff[iMarker_Monitoring] =
2889 SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring] / (SurfaceCoeff.CD[iMarker_Monitoring] + EPS);
2890 SurfaceCoeff.CFx[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceViscCoeff.CFx[iMarker_Monitoring];
2891 SurfaceCoeff.CFy[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceViscCoeff.CFy[iMarker_Monitoring];
2892 SurfaceCoeff.CFz[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceViscCoeff.CFz[iMarker_Monitoring];
2893 SurfaceCoeff.CMx[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceViscCoeff.CMx[iMarker_Monitoring];
2894 SurfaceCoeff.CMy[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceViscCoeff.CMy[iMarker_Monitoring];
2895 SurfaceCoeff.CMz[iMarker_Monitoring] += SurfaceViscCoeff.CMz[iMarker_Monitoring];
2896 }
2897
2898 Buffet_Monitoring(geometry, config);
2899
2900}
2901
2902template<class V, ENUM_REGIME R>
2903su2double CFVMFlowSolverBase<V,R>::EvaluateCommonObjFunc(const CConfig& config) const {
2904
2905 su2double objFun = 0.0;
2906
2907 /*--- Loop over all monitored markers, add to the 'combo' objective ---*/
2908
2909 for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < config.GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker++) {
2910
2911 const auto weight = config.GetWeight_ObjFunc(iMarker);
2912
2913 switch (config.GetKind_ObjFunc(iMarker)) {
2914 case DRAG_COEFFICIENT:
2915 objFun += weight * SurfaceCoeff.CD[iMarker];
2916 break;
2917 case LIFT_COEFFICIENT:
2918 objFun += weight * SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker];
2919 break;
2920 case SIDEFORCE_COEFFICIENT:
2921 objFun += weight * SurfaceCoeff.CSF[iMarker];
2922 break;
2923 case MOMENT_X_COEFFICIENT:
2924 objFun += weight * SurfaceCoeff.CMx[iMarker];
2925 break;
2926 case MOMENT_Y_COEFFICIENT:
2927 objFun += weight * SurfaceCoeff.CMy[iMarker];
2928 break;
2929 case MOMENT_Z_COEFFICIENT:
2930 objFun += weight * SurfaceCoeff.CMz[iMarker];
2931 break;
2932 case FORCE_X_COEFFICIENT:
2933 objFun += weight * SurfaceCoeff.CFx[iMarker];
2934 break;
2935 case FORCE_Y_COEFFICIENT:
2936 objFun += weight * SurfaceCoeff.CFy[iMarker];
2937 break;
2938 case FORCE_Z_COEFFICIENT:
2939 objFun += weight * SurfaceCoeff.CFz[iMarker];
2940 break;
2941 case TOTAL_HEATFLUX:
2942 objFun += weight * Surface_HF_Visc[iMarker];
2943 break;
2944 case MAXIMUM_HEATFLUX:
2945 objFun += weight * Surface_MaxHF_Visc[iMarker];
2946 break;
2947 default:
2948 break;
2949 }
2950 }
2951
2952 /*--- The following are not per-surface, and so to avoid that they are
2953 double-counted when multiple surfaces are specified, they have been
2954 placed outside of the loop above. In addition, multi-objective mode is
2955 also disabled for these objective functions (error thrown at start). ---*/
2956
2957 const auto weight = config.GetWeight_ObjFunc(0);
2958
2959 switch (config.GetKind_ObjFunc(0)) {
2960 case EFFICIENCY:
2961 objFun += weight * TotalCoeff.CEff;
2962 break;
2963 case INVERSE_DESIGN_PRESSURE:
2964 objFun += weight * Total_CpDiff;
2965 break;
2966 case INVERSE_DESIGN_HEATFLUX:
2967 objFun += weight * Total_HeatFluxDiff;
2968 break;
2969 case EQUIVALENT_AREA:
2970 objFun += weight*Total_CEquivArea;
2971 break;
2972 case THRUST_COEFFICIENT:
2973 objFun += weight * TotalCoeff.CT;
2974 break;
2975 case TORQUE_COEFFICIENT:
2976 objFun += weight * TotalCoeff.CQ;
2977 break;
2978 case FIGURE_OF_MERIT:
2979 objFun += weight * TotalCoeff.CMerit;
2980 break;
2981 case SURFACE_TOTAL_PRESSURE:
2982 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_TotalPressure(0);
2983 break;
2984 case SURFACE_STATIC_PRESSURE:
2985 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_Pressure(0);
2986 break;
2987 case SURFACE_STATIC_TEMPERATURE:
2988 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_Temperature(0);
2989 break;
2990 case SURFACE_MASSFLOW:
2991 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_MassFlow(0);
2992 break;
2993 case SURFACE_UNIFORMITY:
2994 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_Uniformity(0);
2995 break;
2996 case SURFACE_SECONDARY:
2997 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_SecondaryStrength(0);
2998 break;
2999 case SURFACE_MOM_DISTORTION:
3000 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_MomentumDistortion(0);
3001 break;
3002 case SURFACE_SECOND_OVER_UNIFORM:
3003 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_SecondOverUniform(0);
3004 break;
3005 case SURFACE_PRESSURE_DROP:
3006 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_PressureDrop(0);
3007 break;
3008 case SURFACE_SPECIES_0:
3009 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_Species_0(0);
3010 break;
3011 case SURFACE_SPECIES_VARIANCE:
3012 objFun += weight * config.GetSurface_Species_Variance(0);
3013 break;
3014 case CUSTOM_OBJFUNC:
3015 objFun += weight * Total_Custom_ObjFunc;
3016 break;
3017 default:
3018 break;
3019 }
3020
3021 return objFun;
3022}
3023
3024template <class V, ENUM_REGIME FlowRegime>
3025void CFVMFlowSolverBase<V, FlowRegime>::ComputeAxisymmetricAuxGradients(CGeometry *geometry, const CConfig* config) {
3026
3027 /*--- Loop through all points to set the auxvargrad --*/
3028 SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
3029 for (auto iPoint = 0ul; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
3030 su2double yCoord = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1);
3031 su2double yVelocity = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,1);
3032 su2double xVelocity = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,0);
3033 su2double Total_Viscosity = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint) + nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
3034
3035 if (yCoord > EPS){
3036 su2double nu_v_on_y = Total_Viscosity*yVelocity/yCoord;
3037 nodes->SetAuxVar(iPoint, 0, nu_v_on_y);
3038 nodes->SetAuxVar(iPoint, 1, nu_v_on_y*yVelocity);
3039 nodes->SetAuxVar(iPoint, 2, nu_v_on_y*xVelocity);
3040 }
3041 }
3042 END_SU2_OMP_FOR
3043
3044 /*--- Compute the auxiliary variable gradient with GG or WLS. ---*/
3045 if (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method() == GREEN_GAUSS) {
3046 SetAuxVar_Gradient_GG(geometry, config);
3047 }
3048 if (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method() == WEIGHTED_LEAST_SQUARES) {
3049 SetAuxVar_Gradient_LS(geometry, config);
3050 }
3051}
